  <evidenceContent rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">You can play your part in safeguarding your personal information by not disclosing your login password or account information to anybody unless such person is duly authorized by you. Whenever you log in the Zepp App, particularly on somebody else`s mobile phones or on public Internet terminals, you should always log out at the end of your session.</evidenceContent>
